12/18/2008: Fixed a bug where if both CC and LL used "fork" method the child processes could stay on even after the connection was dropped (0.98)

12/17/2008: Fixed a bug where CC node if used with "fork" method could create zombie processes

11/29/2008: Added some fault tolerancy and security fixes, such as we drop 
	    an incomming connection from CC if it's not coming from the 
	    same IP as control connection or if no client is waiting (v0.96)

11/24/2008: Added multiple concurrent connection support (v0.95)

11/17/2008: Added support for host_access (aka libwrap)

11/17/2008: Initial code release (v0.90)

